The range of reason why they go is wide from a common cold to more serious terminal illnesses. What many American's do not know in the case of the doctor can hurt them.  MDSmartSearch.com is an online tool created to give individuals the information they need to make well informed decisions about their healthcare providers. MDSmartSearch.com helps individuals accomplish this in many ways: *The latest health care provider demographics. *The latest report from the government about sanctioned health care providers. *The most popular medical terms. *Quality information on prescription drugs and their side effects. *Medical images database to help individuals self-diagnose and talk with their doctor. *Hourly updates on health care news, blogs, videos, podcasts, journals, and more. For health care providers, it allows you to keep a pulse on what other individuals are understanding about you and your medical background. Health care providers are encouraged to keep their profile complete and accurate to help the communities they serve.

Full Description: Spatclash.com is a global technology company that allows for disputes/SPATS to be resolved by the opinion of others through an online video voting process. Our goal is to provide an entertaining and effective way for people to resolve disputes.  Anyone can post a video featuring their self telling their side of a SPAT and invite the individual they are arguing with to defend their position. Once both parties have posted their side of the SPAT, people all over the world can weigh in on who is right by voting and leaving comments. When the voting period selected by the SPAT initiator is over, a winner will be declared based on the number of votes received by each participant.  We realize that Spatclash.com will not fully resolve a dispute between individuals. We hope that it will offer another avenue for people to effectively and enjoyably resolve their dispute through the resolution process at Spatclash.com
